%F A061168 a(n) = Sum_{k=1..n} floor(log_2(k)) = (n+1)*floor(log_2(n)) - 2*(2^floor(log_2(n)) - 1). - Diego Torres (torresvillarroel(AT)hotmail.com), Oct 29 2002
